result.name: Pixel Dark Souls - Roblox
result.description: A sword that starts the bonfire means it's dark souls. Browser Warning: The cost of keeping the quality and speed is that it won't appear on Microsoft Edge, a price that I'm willing to pay, switch to any other major browser that supports avif files for it to appear. Lag may also be present due to it being animated. Credits to >an imgur poster, who labelled it as Irithyll of the Boreal Valley from Dark Souls 3<. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
result.notes: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi.
